N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2813.5 - Notification

State Regulations
(a) The
commissioner shall notify the applicant in writing as to the status of the
application. (b) The commissioner
shall render one of the following decisions: (1)
approved as submitted; (2)
approved conditionally; or
(3)
disapproved. Notes
